===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|羊|火|alt2=灬|t1=[[caprid]]|t2=fire|ls=ic}} – a lamb being cooked on a fire. The definition may have come from animals like lambs being apt for cooking and eating.

According to the {{w|Shuowen Jiezi}}, {{Han compound|ls=psc|羊|照|c1=s|c2=p|abb2=yes|nocap=yes}}.

